            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "Update: I have fixed it by adding the following to my `init.vim`, as per [this comment](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/14586#issuecomment-939946909).\r\n\r\n```\r\nlet g:python3_host_prog = \"$PYENV_ROOT/shims/python3\"\r\n```",
